      <t>This document specifies requirements for an IPv6 Customer Edge (CE) router.  Specifically, the current version of this document focuses on the basic provisioning of an IPv6 CE router and the provisioning of IPv6 hosts attached to it.  This document is not an Internet Standards Track specification; it is published for informational purposes.
